    <p>Common issues include delayed payments, high conversion fees, limited gateway access, and the hassle of chasing invoices. Payxem simplifies the entire process: create a professional invoice, share a payment link, and get paid directly. Your funds are held securely and released to your wallet after clearance, with full transparency on fees and processing times.</p>

    <p>Whether you are a graphic designer, web developer, content writer, or any freelancer who invoices international clients, Payxem gives you a reliable payment gateway for freelancers with low platform fees (2.9% + $0.30), multi-currency support, and a clean dashboard to manage everything in one place.</p>
